---
import smile from '@/assets/smile.svg';
import arancini from '@/assets/arancini.png';
import futbol from '@/assets/futbol.png';
import surf from '@/assets/surf.png';
import bosque from '@/assets/bosque.png';

import arrow1 from '@/assets/arrow-c-1.svg';
import arrow2 from '@/assets/arrow-c-2.svg';
import arrow3 from '@/assets/arrow-c-3.svg';

import kala1 from '@/assets/kala.png';
import kala2 from '@/assets/kala2.png';
import kala3 from '@/assets/kala3.png';


---
<section class="about-me" id="about-me">
  <img class="about-me__image" src={smile.src} alt="box" />
  <h2 class="about-me__title">Detrás de los píxeles</h2>

  <div class="about-me__text about-me__text--1">
    <p>
      Y, ahora te dejo un pedacito de mi yo real.
    </p>
    <p>Bienvenidx a mi mundo.</p>
    <br/>
    <p>Nací en Madrid, la ciudad que nunca deja de inspirarme con su mezcla de historia, vida urbana y rincones sorprendentes.</p>
    <br/>
    <p>Soy apasionada del fútbol (corro detrás del balón en mi equipo), si hay olas, me verás surfeando️ y si hay una montaña, seguro que estoy explorando.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-me__pictures">
    
    <img class="about-me__pictures__arrow about-me__pictures__arrow--1" src={arrow1.src} alt="arrow" />
    <img class="about-me__pictures__arrow about-me__pictures__arrow--2" src={arrow2.src} alt="arrow" />
    <img class="about-me__pictures__arrow about-me__pictures__arrow--3" src={arrow3.src} alt="arrow" />


    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--1" src={arancini.src} alt="arancini">
    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--2" src={futbol.src} alt="futbol">
    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--3" src={surf.src} alt="surf">
    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--4" src={bosque.src} alt="bosque">

  </div>
  <div class="about-me__text about-me__text--2">
    <p>Y no estoy sola en estas locuras.</p>
    <br/>
    <p>Esta es mi compañera de vida; Kala. Ella es mi copiloto oficial, mi crítica de diseño silenciosa y la que asegura que nunca pierdo la energía para la siguiente aventura.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="about-me__pictures">
    
    <img class="about-me__pictures__arrow-2 about-me__pictures__arrow-2--1" src={arrow1.src} alt="arrow" />
    <img class="about-me__pictures__arrow-2 about-me__pictures__arrow-2--2" src={arrow2.src} alt="arrow" />


    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--5" src={kala1.src} alt="arancini">
    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--6" src={kala2.src} alt="futbol">
    <img class="about-me__pictures__photo about-me__pictures__photo--7" src={kala3.src} alt="bosque">

  </div>
</section>
<style lang="scss" scoped>
